---
// src/pages/projects/project-7.astro
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Seventh Project" backgroundColor="#1d1c19">
  <main class="project-detail-container">
    <article class="project-detail" transition:name="project-7">
      <a href="/projects" class="back-link">
        <span class="arrow">←</span>
        <span>back to projects</span>
      </a>
      <div class="project-header">
        <h1>Seventh Project</h1>
        <span class="tag">Rust</span>
      </div>

      <p class="project-intro">A high-performance systems project.</p>

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This is a Rust systems application that demonstrates memory safety,
          concurrency, performance optimization, and low-level system
          programming.
        </p>

        <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
        <div class="project-tech">
          <span>Rust</span>
          <span>Tokio</span>
          <span>Serde</span>
          <span>Actix Web</span>
          <span>Cargo</span>
          <span>Clap</span>
        </div>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Memory-safe concurrent programming</li>
          <li>Async runtime with Tokio</li>
          <li>High-performance web server</li>
          <li>Zero-cost abstractions</li>
          <li>Pattern matching and error handling</li>
          <li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Challenges & Solutions</h2>
        <p>
          One of the main challenges was managing ownership and borrowing in
          complex data structures. We solved this by using smart pointers like
          Rc and Arc, and carefully designing the data flow to minimize clones.
        </p>

        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="#" class="project-link-btn primary">
            <span>Live Demo</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="project-link-btn">
            <span>View Code</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .project-detail-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .back-link {
    position: absolute;
    top: -3rem;
    left: 0;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    /* color: #FFE4AF; */
    color: #c5c9c5;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: "Fira Code", "FiraCode Nerd Font", monospace;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    z-index: 10;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    /* color: #EC753A; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
  }

  .arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-detail {
    /* background: #412E20; */
    background: #1d1c19;
    /* border: 3px solid #DA9F5F; */
    border: 3px solid #8ba4b0;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .project-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    /* color: #FFE4AF; */
    color: #c5c9c5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tag {
    /* background: #DA9F5F; */
    background: #8ba4b0;
    /* color: #342331; */
    color: #0f0f14;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    /* border: 1px solid #EC753A; */
    border: 1px solid #8ba4b0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .project-intro {
    /* color: #DA9F5F; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-content h2 {
    /* color: #FFE4AF; */
    color: #c5c9c5;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-content p {
    /* color: #DA9F5F; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-tech {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-tech span {
    /* background: rgba(218, 159, 95, 0.2); */
    background: rgba(139, 164, 176, 0.2);
    /* color: #DA9F5F; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    /* border: 1px solid #DA9F5F; */
    border: 1px solid #8ba4b0;
  }

  .project-content ul {
    /* color: #DA9F5F; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .project-link-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    /* color: #EC753A; */
    color: #8ba4b0;
    /* border: 2px solid #EC753A; */
    border: 2px solid #8ba4b0;
    padding: 1rem 1.75rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: "Fira Code", "FiraCode Nerd Font", monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .project-link-btn.primary {
    /* background: #EC753A; */
    background: #8ba4b0;
    /* color: #342331; */
    color: #0f0f14;
  }

  .project-link-btn:hover {
    /* background: #EC753A; */
    background: #8ba4b0;
    /* color: #342331; */
    color: #0f0f14;
  }

  .project-link-btn.primary:hover {
    /* background: #DA9F5F; */
    background: #8ba4b0;
    /* border-color: #DA9F5F; */
    border-color: #8ba4b0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-detail-container {
      padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      top: -2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .project-detail {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .project-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .project-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .project-link-btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
